diagram application "Theme showcase — sand"
style { theme: sand }

actor-group TEAM "Team" {
  actor DEV "Developer"
  actor OPS "Operator"
}

application CORE "Core platform" {
  module API "API service"
  module JOBS "Job runner"
}

queue BUS "Message broker"

datastore DB "Primary database"

external PAY "Payment provider"


DEV  -> API (HTTPS, JSON)
API  -> DB (SQL)
API  -> BUS (AMQP)
BUS  -> JOBS (AMQP)
API  -> PAY (HTTPS)
OPS  -> JOBS
JOBS -> DB (SQL)
